The '''Rhyde'vak''', also known as the '''Tempest Ocean''' in [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]], was a body of [[Water/Legends|water]] on the [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworld]] of the [[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] [[Species/Legends|species]], [[Bothawui/Legends|Bothawui]]. [[Blee'starn]] was located in this ocean.

